<h2 id="time-signature">Time signature</h2>

<p>Understand that this song has 6 counts per each measure. Iâ€™ll explain more about this later (within strumming section), but itâ€™s important to understand when looking at the chord progression - and understanding how long you stay on each chord.</p>

